00:35:29.230 --> 00:35:32.760
We would like them to
filter this stuff out.

00:35:32.760 --> 00:35:36.200
So it is the policy, and
this is part of the law,

00:35:36.200 --> 00:35:38.450
of the US that there
should be filtering.

00:35:38.450 --> 00:35:42.480
And we want to encourage parents
and ISPs and everybody to keep

00:35:42.490 --> 00:35:45.000
this smut off the network.

00:35:45.006 --> 00:35:47.130
On the other hand, that
was right after the Prodigy

00:35:47.130 --> 00:35:49.530
