00:42:33.560 --> 00:42:35.600
You can argue whether or
not it is a good idea,

00:42:35.600 --> 00:42:37.558
but there is nothing
unconstitutional about it.

00:42:37.560 --> 00:42:39.440
This thing is still
part of US law.

